OL,3,C'Worrying trends' in the number of
OL,4,Cdeaths from alcohol
OL,6,FLatest figures on substance misuse
OL,7,Ffrom Public Health Wales (PHW) have
OL,8,Frevealed "worrying trends" in alcohol-
OL,9,Frelated deaths and hospital admissions
OL,10,Facross the country.
OL,12,FAlcohol-specific deaths ` those from
OL,13,Fconditions wholly or partially caused
OL,14,Fby alcohol ` increased to a new record
OL,15,Fhigh with 562 fatalities recorded in
OL,16,FWales in 2023, marking a 15.6%
OL,17,Fincrease from the previous year (486)
OL,18,Fand a significant rise from 10 years
OL,19,Fbefore (351 in 2014). Of the alcohol-
OL,20,Fspecific deaths in 2023, nearly two
OL,21,Fthirds (64.8%) involved males.
