OL,3,C'Worrying trends' in the number of
OL,4,Cdeaths from alcohol
OL,6,FDeprivation plays a significant role
OL,7,Fwith individuals from the most
OL,8,Fdeprived areas in Wales 2.8 times more
OL,9,Flikely to be admitted for alcohol-
OL,10,Fspecific conditions than those from
OL,11,Fthe least deprived areas.
OL,13,FProf Rick Lines, Head of the Substance
OL,14,FMisuse Programme at Public Health
OL,15,FWales, said: "The impacts of the
OL,16,Fharmful use of alcohol continue to be
OL,17,Fa concern across Wales, both in terms
OL,18,Fof drug related deaths in which
OL,19,Falcohol is a factor as well as the
OL,20,Flong-term health effects of alcohol.
